reviewText: This video is a phenomenal starting point for those serious about learning Kenpo. The instructor has many years of experience. I would highly recommend this video with the expectation that you continue with the rest of the series, as this is the framework to learn the martial art. Thanks to the producer for making this available!
This is a well done video of instruction for distance learning!  This is a system of American Kenpo combined with Jujitsu techniques to cover both on on feet and off feet techniques!
